Introduction

eite is a Japanese-South Korean girl group under EVA ENTERTAINMENT. The group debuted on November 3, 2023, with their first album "Independent Woman".

The original lineup of the group consisted of members Yuisa, Ari, Rena, Yujin, Reo, Sia, and Chaehyun. On August 18, 2024, it was announced by the agency that the seven members had terminated their contracts and left the group.

The group is set to return with new members while still maintaining the same concept they originally had.
